---

## ğŸ“Œ Step 3: Java Application

```java
package com.message;

public class MessageApp {

    public static String getMessage() {
        return "Learning DevOps step by step makes life easier!";
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println(getMessage());
    }
}
```

---

## ğŸ“Œ Step 4: Unit Test

```java
package com.message;

import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;
import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertEquals;

public class MessageAppTest {

    @Test
    void verifyMessage() {
        assertEquals(
            "Learning DevOps step by step makes life easier!",
            MessageApp.getMessage()
        );
    }
}
```

---

## ğŸ“Œ Step 5: Maven Build File

```xml
<project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0">
  <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>
  <groupId>com.message</groupId>
  <artifactId>java-application</artifactId>
  <version>1.0</version>

  <properties>
    <maven.compiler.source>21</maven.compiler.source>
    <maven.compiler.target>21</maven.compiler.target>
  </properties>

  <dependencies>
    <dependency>
      <groupId>org.junit.jupiter</groupId>
      <artifactId>junit-jupiter</artifactId>
      <version>5.9.3</version>
      <scope>test</scope>
    </dependency>
  </dependencies>

  <build>
    <plugins>
      <plugin>
        <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
        <artifactId>maven-jar-plugin</artifactId>
        <version>3.3.0</version>
        <configuration>
          <archive>
            <manifest>
              <mainClass>com.message.MessageApp</mainClass>
            </manifest>
          </archive>
        </configuration>
      </plugin>
    </plugins>
  </build>
</project>
```

---

## ğŸ“Œ Step 6: Build & Test

```bash
mvn clean package
```

---

## ğŸ“Œ Step 7: Run Locally

```bash
java -jar target/java-application-1.0.jar
```

---

## ğŸ“Œ Step 8: Dockerfile

```dockerfile
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine
WORKDIR /app
COPY target/java-application-1.0.jar app.jar
CMD ["java","-jar","app.jar"]
```

---

## ğŸ“Œ Step 9: Docker Run

```bash
docker build -t java-message-app .
docker run --rm java-message-app
```

---

## ğŸ“Œ Step 10: Docker Compose

```yaml
version: '3'
services:
  message-app:
    image: java-message-app
```

```bash
docker-compose up --build
docker-compose down
```

---

## ğŸ“Œ Step 11: Jenkins Pipeline

```groovy
pipeline {
    agent any

    tools {
        maven 'maven-3'
    }

    stages {
        stage('Build & Test') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn clean package'
            }
        }
        stage('Docker Build') {
            steps {
                sh 'docker build -t java-message-app .'
            }
        }
        stage('Docker Run') {
            steps {
                sh 'docker run --rm java-message-app'
            }
        }
    }
}
```

---

## ğŸ“Œ Step 12: GitHub Push

```bash
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Java CI/CD beginner project"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin <repo-url>
git push -u origin main
```

